---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Contact Us" description="Get in touch with PlainInfluence. Questions, feedback, or data corrections."
  breadcrumbs={[{ name: 'Home', href: '/' }, { name: 'Contact' }]}>
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-8">
    <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold">Contact Us</h1>

    <div class="mt-6 space-y-4 text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)] leading-relaxed">
      <p>Found a campaign contribution figure that does not align with FEC records, or noticed a lobbying disclosure that seems miscategorized? Journalists, researchers, and civically engaged citizens who flag issues help maintain the integrity of this political accountability database.</p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-[var(--color-foreground)]">Email</h2>
      <p>
        The fastest way to reach us is by email:
        <a href="mailto:hello@plaininfluence.com" class="text-[var(--color-accent)] hover:underline">hello@plaininfluence.com</a>
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-[var(--color-foreground)]">Data Corrections</h2>
      <p>If you believe any data displayed on PlainInfluence is inaccurate, please email us with the specific page URL and the correction. We source our data from FEC, Senate LDA, and USAspending.gov and update when new data is published.</p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-[var(--color-foreground)]">About PlainInfluence</h2>
      <p>PlainInfluence is a project by <a href="https://kiznis.studio" class="text-[var(--color-accent)] hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Kiznis Studio</a>. We build free, open data tools powered by official government and public datasets.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
